Anonymous users cannot:
\n- Create groups;
\n- Sync groups and devices with the server;
\n- Manage groups and devices in a personal dashboard on the website.

OsmAnd shows photos from several sources:
\nOpenPlaceReviews - POI photos;
\nMapillary - street-level imagery;
\nWeb / Wikimedia - POI photos as per OpenStreetMap data.
